description: Search result fixtures for Acme Corp company research
raw_mcp_response:
1. Acme Corp | About Us
   URL: https://www.acmecorp.com/about
   Summary: Acme Corp is a leading enterprise software company specializing in cloud-based data analytics solutions. Founded in 2015, we help businesses transform their data into actionable insights.

2. Acme Corp raises $50M Series C to expand AI capabilities - TechCrunch
   URL: https://techcrunch.com/2024/09/15/acme-corp-series-c
   Summary: Acme Corp announced today it has raised $50 million in Series C funding led by Sequoia Capital. The company plans to use the funds to expand its machine learning and AI capabilities.

3. Acme Corp Careers - Join Our Team
   URL: https://careers.acmecorp.com
   Summary: Explore career opportunities at Acme Corp. We're hiring engineers, data scientists, and product managers to help us build the future of data analytics.

4. Acme Corp Reviews | Glassdoor
   URL: https://www.glassdoor.com/acme-corp-reviews
   Summary: See what employees say about working at Acme Corp. 4.2 star rating based on 342 reviews. Pros: Great culture, competitive compensation. Cons: Fast-paced environment.

5. Acme Corp - LinkedIn
   URL: https://www.linkedin.com/company/acme-corp
   Summary: Acme Corp | 2,500 followers on LinkedIn. Enterprise data analytics platform trusted by Fortune 500 companies. Headquarters: San Francisco, CA.
